  "about_app": "Barnaamijka \"Quraanka Kariimka - Maktabadda Hikmah\" waa barnaamij dhammaystiran oo bixiya xulasho ballaaran oo ah sifooyin si loo hagaajiyo khibradda akhriska iyo barashada Quraanka Kariimka. Sifooyinkan waxaa ka mid ah:",
  "@about_app": {
    "type": "text",
    "placeholders": {}
  },
  "about_app2": "Among the most important features of the application :",
  "@about_app2": {
    "type": "text",
    "placeholders": {}
  },
  "about_app3": "۞ Interface casri ah oo fudud in la isticmaalo: Naqshad cusub oo dareen leh oo fududaysa dhex-marista iyo helitaanka dhammaan sifooyinka, iyadoo lagu daray muuqaal cusub oo kalandarka ah iyo awoodda in la daawado kalandarka sanadlaha oo dhan.\n۞ Qaadashada daabacaadda Majma'ul Malik Fahd: App-ku wuxuu ku tiirsan yahay daabacaadda Majma'ul Malik Fahd ee Mushafka, oo caan ku ah saxnaanta iyo kalsoonida.\n۞ Akhris is-dhexgal ah oo dhammaystiran: Khibrad akhris dabacsan—qaabka mushaf (bogag) ama qaabka aayad keliya—iyadoo la taageerayo isdhexgal buuxa oo la leh qoraalka.\n۞ Dhageysi horumarsan: Awoodda in la dhageysto aayadaha iyo suuradaha codadka qaar ka mid ah qurraa'da, iyadoo la soo bandhigayo aayadaha hadda socda inta lagu jiro ciyaarista, iyo sidoo kale in eray kasta si gooni ah loo dhageysto si waxbarashadu u sahlanaato.\n۞ Baadhitaan iyo hagid degdeg ah: Baadhitaan degdeg ah oo ku jira aayadaha Qur'aanka oo leh awoodda in si toos ah loogu boodo suuradda ama bogga la rabo, iyo hagid fudud oo u dhexeeya suuradaha.\n۞ Tafsiir iyo maktabad Islaami ah: Helitaanka ururin tafsiir iyo tarjumaad ah, iyo maktabad Islaami ah oo dhammaystiran oo ka kooban kutubta xadiiska iyo tafsiirka.\n۞ Tajwiid iyo axkaamtiisa: Taageero lagu muujinayo tajwiidka iyo axkaamtiisa si cad, iyadoo lagu daray Qira'aadka Tobanka si loo ballaariyo fahamka hababka qira'ada.\n۞ Falanqayn luqadeed horumarsan: Muujinta tasriifka iyo i'raabka eray kasta, taas oo ka caawisa faham qoto dheer oo macnayaasha luqadeed ee Qur'aanka.\n۞ Aayadaha isu-eg: Sifo gaar ah oo lagu soo bandhigo aayadaha isu-eg si loo fududeeyo xifdinta iyo dib-u-eegista.\n۞ Maareynta akhriska iyo xifdinta: Awoodda in la sameeyo bookmarks aayado iyo bogag si dib loogu noqdo wakhti kasta.\n۞ Akhrinta calaamadaha waqf: Sharaxidda calaamadaha waqf si ay u caawiyaan akhris sax ah.\n۞ Adkaar Hisnul Muslim: Qayb dhammaystiran oo adkaar ah, leh favori iyo marin degdeg ah oo u dhexeeya qaybaha.\n۞ Habayn muuqaalka: Taageero beddelka qaababka midabka, oo ay ku jirto habka madow, si akhrisku u noqdo mid raaxo leh.\n۞ Soo dejin iyo isticmaal offline: Soo dejinta suuradaha iyo dhageysiga dambe adigoon internet lahayn.\n\nSifooyinkani waxay ka dhigayaan app-ka \"Quraanka Kariimka - Maktabadda Hikmah\" madal dhammaystiran oo isku darta akhris, dhageysi, tafsiir iyo waxbarasho, kana dhiga khibrad iimaan iyo aqoon leh oo qani ah isla markaana fudud in la isticmaalo.",
  "@about_app3": {
    "type": "text",
    "placeholders": {}
  },
